<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 22:05:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊拉克亲民兵组织 Telegram 频道发布人质视频，显示在伊拉克失踪的以色列学者伊丽莎白·楚尔科夫 (Elizabeth Tsurkov)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/iraqi-telegram-channels-publish-video-of-israeli-hostage-elizabeth-tsurkov/0000018b-ca84-dd30-a5ff-efe53e170000</link><description>37 岁的楚尔科夫被拍摄到她呼吁结束加沙战斗，并要求采取行动释放她。楚尔科夫拥有以色列和俄罗斯双重国籍，自三月以来一直被伊拉克什叶派武装组织卡塔伊布真主党关押。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 21:37:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/iraqi-telegram-channels-publish-video-of-israeli-hostage-elizabeth-tsurkov/0000018b-ca84-dd30-a5ff-efe53e170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长要求将所有机密材料违反程序发送至总理办公室</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-attorney-general-demands-to-see-all-classified-material-sent-to-pms-office/0000018b-ca64-d8c7-a59b-df6d43550000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的幕僚长试图违反政府规定收集国家安全机密文件，此举显然是为了避免因 10 月 7 日的灾难而受到指责</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 21:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-attorney-general-demands-to-see-all-classified-material-sent-to-pms-office/0000018b-ca64-d8c7-a59b-df6d43550000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长埃利·科恩估计，以色列还有两到三周的时间才能加大国际压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/fm-cohen-israel-has-between-two-and-three-weeks-before-international-pressure-intensifies/0000018b-ca38-df9a-ab8b-def8d8c00000</link><description>以色列外交部长伊莱·科恩承认国际社会对加沙战斗暂停的压力越来越大，他表示“10月7日大屠杀的震惊已经减轻”，并且“最近几天，世界媒体主要展示来自加沙的图像”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 20:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/fm-cohen-israel-has-between-two-and-three-weeks-before-international-pressure-intensifies/0000018b-ca38-df9a-ab8b-def8d8c00000</guid></item><item><title>《沉默之声》的讽刺成为以色列生活的完美隐喻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-13/ty-article/.highlight/satirical-take-on-the-sound-of-silence-becomes-perfect-metaphor-for-life-in-israel/0000018b-c9e1-df9a-ab8b-dfe9bac40000</link><description>《离开这里》是一首 10 月 7 日之后的以色列歌曲，以 60 年代经典音乐为背景，立即成为反政府热门歌曲。但这首歌并不是对忧郁情绪的不敬的转折；只是阴郁</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 20:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-13/ty-article/.highlight/satirical-take-on-the-sound-of-silence-becomes-perfect-metaphor-for-life-in-israel/0000018b-c9e1-df9a-ab8b-dfe9bac40000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫医院发言人在解救哈马斯人质后举行有争议的新闻发布会，被传唤参加解散前听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-hospital-spokesperson-summoned-after-freed-hostages-presser/0000018b-c9fb-df9a-ab8b-dffb47b50000</link><description>在伊奇洛夫医院工作了 14 年的阿维·肖山 (Avi Shoshan) 因协助召开新闻发布会而被强制休假，约切韦德·利夫什茨 (Yocheved Lifshitz) 表示，哈马斯对她“非常友好”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-hospital-spokesperson-summoned-after-freed-hostages-presser/0000018b-c9fb-df9a-ab8b-dffb47b50000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列其他地区相比，贝都因学校拥有防空洞的可能性要小得多</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-schools-are-much-less-likely-to-have-bomb-shelters-compared-to-rest-of-israel/0000018b-c9a5-df9a-ab8b-dfed716a0000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙与哈马斯交战，附近内盖夫数以万计的贝都因儿童就读于缺乏避难所或避难所不符合民防标准的学校</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-schools-are-much-less-likely-to-have-bomb-shelters-compared-to-rest-of-israel/0000018b-c9a5-df9a-ab8b-dfed716a0000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙战争的进行，以色列定居者袭击巴勒斯坦人，并在约旦河西岸创造了新的现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-attack-palestinians-and-create-a-new-reality-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-c965-dd8b-abbf-dfff567c0000</link><description>当以色列国防军和辛贝特在加沙地带忙碌时，约旦河西岸定居者却利用战争入侵私人土地、攻击巴勒斯坦人并用军事武器武装自己</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 18:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-attack-palestinians-and-create-a-new-reality-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-c965-dd8b-abbf-dfff567c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么我的左翼非政府组织这次不支持与哈马斯停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-my-leftist-ngo-wont-back-a-cease-fire-with-hamas-this-time/0000018b-c95d-d353-a3fb-cffd1e020000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 18:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-my-leftist-ngo-wont-back-a-cease-fire-with-hamas-this-time/0000018b-c95d-d353-a3fb-cffd1e020000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的犹太巨额捐助者正在犯一个灾难性的错误</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trumps-jewish-megadonors-are-making-a-disastrous-mistake/0000018b-c953-dd8b-abbf-dfffcb600000</link><description>在反犹太主义在美国爆发、以色列面临生存威胁之际，特朗普的犹太辩护者为什么会支持一个容易受到共和党孤立主义抬头的普京谄媚者、一个对以色列没有真正信念的、煽动犹太人的活生生的引擎呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 18:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trumps-jewish-megadonors-are-making-a-disastrous-mistake/0000018b-c953-dd8b-abbf-dfffcb600000</guid></item><item><title>“问题在于你，而不是哈马斯”：人质家属猛烈抨击以色列政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/families-find-israeli-government-at-fault-for-kidnappings-and-failed-return-of-hostages/0000018b-c8fe-d485-ab9b-ecffc5f10000</link><description>在加沙被扣押的人质的亲属表示，当哈马斯恐怖分子 10 月 7 日渗透到以色列社区时，以色列军队并没有在那里保护他们。许多人认为，没有进行认真的谈判来释放他们的亲属。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 16:46:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/families-find-israeli-government-at-fault-for-kidnappings-and-failed-return-of-hostages/0000018b-c8fe-d485-ab9b-ecffc5f10000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的泰国受害者仍被关押在加沙：“这太野蛮了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/thai-victims-of-hamas-in-gaza-this-is-just-too-barbaric-and-cruel/0000018b-c948-de48-a19b-ebfd62b20000</link><description>10月7日，34名泰国公民被哈马斯武装分子杀害，25名泰国社区成员被绑架。被绑架到拉斯维加斯大道的龚的生活伴侣在泰国的家中希望能得到生命的迹象</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 16:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/thai-victims-of-hamas-in-gaza-this-is-just-too-barbaric-and-cruel/0000018b-c948-de48-a19b-ebfd62b20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝承认巴勒斯坦权力机构是治理加沙的唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-refuses-to-admit-that-the-pa-is-the-only-option-for-governing-gaza/0000018b-c906-d8e8-a79b-ef8e95040000</link><description>以色列总理坚持对加沙建立“以色列安全控制”，但以色列国防军没有能力管理200万平民。巴勒斯坦权力机构是管理巴勒斯坦人日常生活方面唯一具有合法性和经验的机构</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 15:47:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-refuses-to-admit-that-the-pa-is-the-only-option-for-governing-gaza/0000018b-c906-d8e8-a79b-ef8e95040000</guid></item><item><title>“我从没想过反犹太主义可能再次被社会接受”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/i-never-thought-it-was-possible-that-anti-semitism-would-be-socially-acceptable-again/0000018b-c919-da03-a9bf-cd79628d0000</link><description>德国媒体周末在反犹太主义高涨之际纪念水晶之夜。一份左翼报纸还深入探讨了伊斯兰主义者参与当前反以色列示威活动的情况，警告“新一波伊斯兰激进化和暴力”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 15:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/i-never-thought-it-was-possible-that-anti-semitism-would-be-socially-acceptable-again/0000018b-c919-da03-a9bf-cd79628d0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣押的贝都因人质亲属：“这不是一场宗教战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-magazine/bedouin-family-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-this-isnt-a-religious-war/0000018b-c8a8-d485-ab9b-ecf9d0080000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列人家庭：一个特别项目 ■ 在加沙被扣为人质的 239 名以色列人中，阿里·阿尔齐亚德纳 (Ali Alziadna) 有一个兄弟、两个侄子和一个侄女。他和其他贝都因人都明确表示，针对哈马斯的战争不是阿拉伯人针对犹太人的战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 15:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-magazine/bedouin-family-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-this-isnt-a-religious-war/0000018b-c8a8-d485-ab9b-ecf9d0080000</guid></item><item><title>约旦国王阿卜杜拉拒绝以色列占领加沙部分地区的任何计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/update-1-jordans-king-rejects-any-israeli-plan-to-occupy-parts-of-gaza/0000018b-c933-dd8b-abbf-dfff43120000</link><description>约旦国王阿卜杜拉表示，他拒绝以色列占领加沙部分地区或在飞地内建立安全区的任何计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 15:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/update-1-jordans-king-rejects-any-israeli-plan-to-occupy-parts-of-gaza/0000018b-c933-dd8b-abbf-dfff43120000</guid></item><item><title>巴黎反犹太主义抗议活动为法国犹太人注入氧气</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/paris-protest-against-antisemitism-gives-french-jews-an-oxygen-boost/0000018b-c8da-d61e-a39b-dddeeff30000</link><description>周日，法国各地有超过 18 万人示威抗议该国当前的反犹太主义浪潮，巴黎发生的事情既令人鼓舞又令人沮丧</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 14:37:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/paris-protest-against-antisemitism-gives-french-jews-an-oxygen-boost/0000018b-c8da-d61e-a39b-dddeeff30000</guid></item><item><title>所有以色列人都是该死的“殖民主义者”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-all-israeli-babies-colonialist-who-deserve-to-die/0000018b-c87e-d61e-a39b-ddfe0fc10000</link><description>根据后殖民口号，世界分为加害者和受害者：前者不能做正义的事，后者不能做恶事。令人毛骨悚然的是，这种道德盲目性是如何上演的：哈马斯的暴行是可以原谅的，因为“殖民主义”以色列人罪有应得。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 13:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-all-israeli-babies-colonialist-who-deserve-to-die/0000018b-c87e-d61e-a39b-ddfe0fc10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首席拉比呼吁周一设立全球祈祷日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-chief-rabbinate-calls-for-global-day-of-prayer-on-monday/0000018b-c879-d25b-abdf-ddfdc4b40000</link><description>拉比呼吁公众背诵诗篇，并“为以色列国防军士兵的和平祈祷，为伤员康复祈祷，为被绑架和失踪的人祈祷”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 13:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-chief-rabbinate-calls-for-global-day-of-prayer-on-monday/0000018b-c879-d25b-abdf-ddfdc4b40000</guid></item><item><title>ADL 称自加沙战争爆发以来美国反犹太主义事件增加了 300% 以上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/antisemitic-incidents-in-u-s-up-over-300-since-start-of-gaza-war-adl-says/0000018b-c85a-d485-ab9b-ec7babcf0000</link><description>10月7日至11月7日期间发生了832起事件——平均每天28起。其中多起事件发生在美国东北部，其中112起发生在大学校园</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 12:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/antisemitic-incidents-in-u-s-up-over-300-since-start-of-gaza-war-adl-says/0000018b-c85a-d485-ab9b-ec7babcf0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争使以色列创作者与欧洲国际电影节之间的关系紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-strains-ties-between-israeli-creators-and-european-international-film-fests/0000018b-c834-d485-ab9b-ec75990a0000</link><description>由于斯德哥尔摩电影节取消邀请以色列电视节目创作者，艺术总监对支持巴勒斯坦的抗议表示赞赏，并表示他们“必须表明立场”，以色列公共广播公司与电影节断绝了关系</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 11:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-strains-ties-between-israeli-creators-and-european-international-film-fests/0000018b-c834-d485-ab9b-ec75990a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>